This paper deals with knowledge graph embedding, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper proposes a new method for representing hierarchical knowledge, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also involves working with databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR) to evaluate the effectiveness of the proposed method.
